### [FALHA] Sem token de autenticação
# Esperado: 401 UnauthorizedError
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{appointmentIdAbmael}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "completed"
}

###

### [FALHA] Agendamento inexistente
# Esperado: 404 NotFoundError
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{appointmentIdAbmaelInexistente}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessTokenAbmael}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "completed"
}

###

### [FALHA] Status inválido
# Esperado: 422 Validation Error com campo status nos issues
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{appointmentIdAbmael}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessTokenAbmael}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "scheduled"
}

###

### [SUCESSO] Atualizar status para completed
# Esperado: 200 com status completed
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{appointmentIdAbmael}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessTokenAbmael}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "completed"
}

###

### [SUCESSO] Atualizar status para canceled
# Esperado: 200 com status canceled
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{appointmentIdAbmael}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessTokenAbmael}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "canceled"
}

###

### [SUCESSO] Atualizar status para no_show
# Esperado: 200 com status no_show
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{appointmentIdAbmael}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessTokenAbmael}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "no_show"
}

###

### [FALHA] Tentativa de alterar agendamento já finalizado
# Esperado: 409 ConflictError
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{appointmentIdAbmael}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessTokenAbmael}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "completed"
}

###
